{
  "key": 37946,
  "messages": [
    {
      "id": "EternaCitySouthHouse_Text_HowIsYourPokedexComingAlong",
      "en_US": [
        "Oak: Ah, it’s you! Good to see you!\n",
        "How is your Pokédex coming along?\r",
        "Capturing every kind of Pokémon is\n",
        "no easy feat, I’ll grant you that.\r",
        "But I’m sure you can accomplish it!\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "EternaCitySouthHouse_Text_AnAcquaintanceFromKantoHasSentSomethingQuiteInteresting",
      "en_US": [
        "Oak: Ah, yes!\r",
        "An acquaintance from Kanto has sent\n",
        "me something quite interesting.\r",
        "I think you’d make better use of it\n",
        "than I ever could.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "EternaCitySouthHouse_Text_IUnderstandThereIsAPokemonThatEvolvesWhenItIsTradedWhileHoldingThatUpGrade",
      "en_US": [
        "I understand there is a Pokémon that\n",
        "evolves when it is traded while holding\f",
        "that Up-Grade.\r"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "EternaCitySouthHouse_Text_IveHeardThatThereHaveBeenSightingsOfArticunoZapdosAndMoltres",
      "en_US": [
        "Incidentally, and this is an entirely\n",
        "different topic...\r",
        "I’ve heard that there have been\n",
        "sightings of very rare Pokémon.\r",
        "The legendary bird Pokémon: ARTICUNO,\n",
        "ZAPDOS, and MOLTRES!\r",
        "They’ve been spotted at various\n",
        "locations here in Sinnoh, no less!\r",
        "Why, you may be lucky enough to see\n",
        "them yourself in your journeys!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "EternaCitySouthHouse_Text_ArticunoZapdosAndMoltresAreExtremelyRareEvenInKanto",
      "en_US": [
        "Oak: ARTICUNO, ZAPDOS, and MOLTRES\n",
        "are extremely rare even in Kanto.\r",
        "There have been precious few sightings\n",
        "as it is.\r",
        "So why would they be spotted here in\n",
        "Sinnoh of all places?\r",
        "There are still many, many mysteries\n",
        "surrounding Pokémon, it seems!"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "EternaCitySouthHouse_Text_YouveCaughtArticunoZapdosAndMoltresAllowMeToExamineYourPokedex",
      "en_US": [
        "Oak: Ah, it’s you!\n",
        "How goes it?\r",
        "What’s that? You’ve caught ARTICUNO,\n",
        "ZAPDOS, and MOLTRES?!\r",
        "Now that is incredible!\r",
        "Well, then, allow me to examine your\n",
        "Pokédex.\r"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
